  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Thread the cod pieces and tofu onto skewers.",
    "Heat the coconut oil in a large skillet over medium high heat.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger to the skillet and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the skewers to the skillet and cook for 2 minutes on each side.",
    "Transfer the skewers to a baking sheet and bake for 10 minutes.",
    "Brush the skewers with fish sauce during the last 2 minutes of cooking.",
    "Sprinkle the green onions and sesame seeds over the skewers.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste."
